languages.text: "Ирлиэт была обманута, как и мы. Едва ли ее деяние можно назвать подлостью".
"Yrliet was deceived, as we all were. Her actions can hardly be called trickery."

languages.text: 「ユリエットは私たちと同じように騙されていた。彼女の行動は策略とは言い難い」
languages.original_text: "Yrliet was deceived, as we all were. Her actions can hardly be called trickery."

languages.text: “伊莉耶特和我们一样，她也被骗了。她的行为恐怕算不上‘奸计’。”
languages.original_text: "Yrliet was deceived, as we all were. Her actions can hardly be called trickery."

traits.locale_text: “伊莉耶特和我们一样，她也被骗了。她的行为恐怕算不上‘奸计’。”

languages.text: «Engañaron a Yrliet, al igual que a todos nosotros. Sus acciones no constituyen ningún tipo de traición».
languages.original_text: "Yrliet was deceived, as we all were. Her actions can hardly be called trickery."

traits.locale_text: «Engañaron a Yrliet mintieron, al igual que a nosotros. Sus acciones no constituyen ningún tipo de traición».

languages.text: "Yrliet wurde getäuscht, genau wie wir alle. Man kann ihre Taten wohl kaum als Betrug bezeichnen."
languages.original_text: "Yrliet was deceived, as we all were. Her actions can hardly be called trickery."

languages.text: « Yrliet a été trompée, elle aussi. Elle n'a fait preuve d'aucune traîtrise. »

languages.text: "Hepimiz gibi Yrliet de kandırılmış. Bize üçkâğıt etti diyemeyiz."
